OL,5, The Driving and Vehicles Standards     
OL,6, Agency (DVSA) says it has started to   
OL,7, take action against companies          
OL,8, exploiting learner drivers.            
OL,10,FA BBC investigation found that some    
OL,11,Flearner drivers had paid over #200 for 
OL,12,Fa practical driving test - more than   
OL,13,Fdouble the standard fee.               
OL,15,FThe number of times a test can be      
OL,16,Fchanged has been reduced from 10 to the
OL,17,Fpre-pandemic limit of six.             
OL,19,FAccounts not linked to instructors on  
OL,20,Fthe booking system are being removed.  
